---
title: Tray Bake Shawarma Chicken Thighs Bowls with Lemony Roasted Potatoes
description: Leave the pita behind and fill this wondrous bowl with all your favourite shawarma toppings: savoury chicken, creamy garlic dressing, lemony roasted potatoes, fresh tomatoes and bright green parsley!
